data.description: You will be wooed by this country farmhouse's character and charm. The painted hardi exterior blends tastefully with the natural environment. Parking will never be an issue with a generous, gravel area in front of the home. Take advantage of the morning sun on the welcoming, covered front porch. The interior is just lovely with wood laminate flooring, abundant natural light, and large windows that showcase the mature trees that wrap around the home. This lovely home spans over 840 sq ft and features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. The traditional country-style kitchen will be a delight to prepare meals in with ample storage and countertop space. The open-plan kitchen/dining area is the perfect environment for entertaining. The 2 generous bedrooms exude comfort and relaxation. Each room includes laminate wood flooring, a ceiling fan, and an ample sized closet. The light and bright full bath features a single vanity and shower/tub. Sitting on almost an acre, this home enjoys the privacy of the hill country while still being within 7 minutes of shopping, dining, and entertainment in downtown Bastrop. You will love exploring the great outdoors with Bastrop State Park practically on your back doorstep. Perfect to move straight into and enjoy, with plenty of scope to further update in the future!
